wireframe

Class AbstractElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • wireframe.AbstractElement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractWireframeElement, Annotation

    abstract class AbstractElement
extends java.lang.Object
    The AbstractElement class provides some of the basic implementation shared by its subclasses Annotation and AbstractWireframeElement. In particular, it implements moving, resizing, and typing, as well as access to the needed fields for those operations.
